description:
Danny welcomes Leah McSweeney from Bravo's The Real Housewives of New York. They talk about her first season, her evolving relationships, and lots more! The wonderful Raquel Leviss from Vanderpump Rules also calls in to tell us a bit more about herself and her relationships on the show.


Raquel Interview: 27:36ish
